
 This patch permits to use migration options with JobDefs.
 This patch fixes bug #1028.

 Apply the patch to 2.2.7 (and possibly any 2.2.x version with):

 cd <bacula-source>
 patch -p0 <2.2.7-jobdefs-migtype.patch
 ./configure <your-options>
 make
 ...
 make install

